    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Armor for the horse's neck, made of narrow lames articulated together, or of lames alternating with bands of mail.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
